    "This method has proven effective in various domains and could enhance the performance of our model.Figure 11Figure 1 illustrates the architecture of our solution with APP-TGN.",
    "It mainly consists of five main components: Data Collection & Pre-processing, Dynamic Graph Construction, Global Sampling Module, Low-High Filtering Temporal Graph Networks(LHFTGN), Academic Performance Representation & Prediction.Procedures of APP-TGN Data Collection & Pre-processing includes attribution selection, data cleaning, and data transformation.",
